name: Untitled #5
description:
There are rumors about the government paying thugs to burn down old traditional market, before they renovate it. Burning down the old buildings are much cheaper and less hassle than evicting and offering the current shop owners fair compensation.

Reinterpretation of spread 5 from my zine, 29 (2019).

6199 x 4133 | 300 DPI

Original photos, mixed media collage.
